  <summary date="2024-09-12T10:29:57Z" status="Introduced in House">Family Stability and Opportunity Vouchers Act of 2023

This bill establishes a voucher program through which&#160;public housing agencies (PHAs)&#160;shall&#160;offer support services to help families who have children and are&#160;unstably housed, live in an area of concentrated poverty,&#160;or are&#160;at risk of being displaced from an opportunity area for children move to areas with access to high-performing schools or high-quality childcare and early education. The Department of Housing and Urban Development must provide assistance to PHAs on a competitive basis to implement the program.&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;</summary>
